appDesc.message: This extension saves pages to view for later.

appName.message: VIEW LATER - save links in a stack

options_always_open_link_in_current_tab.message: always open links in current tab

options_close_tab.message: close tab automatically, when page is added to the stack

options_display_notifications.message: show notifications when adding a page

options_remove_link.message: remove link automatically from the stack, when it is clicked
